sha256_password
and
caching_sha2_password
plugins, see
Section\ \&6.5.1.2, \(lqSHA-256 Pluggable Authentication\(rq, and
Section\ \&6.5.1.3, \(lqCaching SHA-2 Pluggable Authentication\(rq\&.
